3.4 and z ~ 3. From the comparison\nwith local interstellar studies, we predict a rise of Ar abundances in the\nredshift range from z ~ 2.3 to z=0, at the epoch at which the metagalactic\nfield of galaxies overcomes that of quasars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 3 Mar 2003 11:35:53 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-07"}
